    {
      "id": "3364750c-f3ba-80dc-a773-d0f97f29cc5d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors present CoTutor, which builds on BKT with Signal Processing to deliver adaptive feedback and strategies in an adaptative manner. CoTutor has been deployed to universities and authors report that it outperforms other approaches. ",
